{
  "stem": "9168.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't remember how many interpreters were required for the Doctors' Trial.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was a substantial team of interpreters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the question was being asked by the American prosecutor of the German witness, then we had to wait.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, we knew English, so we wrote the question immediately as we heard the American prosecutor ask it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we had to wait for the interpreters to interpret the answer, given in German, through our earphones.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that took a little bit of time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not know German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I understood that I-- we had all understood that they had to wait until the end of the sentence to get the-- is it the subject?-- before they could interpret.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was interpreting in kind of a-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know what word to use.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to wait.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then there was a fast interpretation of the answer, and we wrote it down in English.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the same token, if the witness was an English witness, or supposing the person was a French witness speaking in French, and the-- being cross-examined by a German attorney in German, it was the same situation.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- we did not know either one of these languages, although the French usually spoke English.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so it was a-- a double-waiting for interpretation, from French to English, from German to English.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by the same token, from German to French, French to German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought it worked quite well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I understood that, in Goering's trial, there were an awful lot of glitches and getting it-- the reporters-- there was a lot of static.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
